{"title":"js获取一个对象的长度","date":"2018-12-06T18:46:00.000Z","link":"post/280","categories":["JS"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:36:58.161Z","content":"<p><strong>对象的长度不能用.length获取，用js原生的Object.keys可以获取到</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> obj = &#123;<span class=\"string\">'name'</span> : <span class=\"string\">'Tom'</span> , <span class=\"string\">'sex'</span> : <span class=\"string\">'male'</span> , <span class=\"string\">'age'</span> : <span class=\"string\">'14'</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> arr = <span class=\"built_in\">Object</span>.keys(obj);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(arr);  <span class=\"comment\">// ['name','sex','age']</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(arr.length);  <span class=\"comment\">//3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"Bootstrap表格内容垂直水平居中","link":"post/281"},"next":{"title":"append()与prepend()的区别","link":"post/279"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/280/"}